I-Grand Maharaja-Maharani Party (ngo-1911) -Ukuba uMlawuli wase-Bhritane u-George V kunye nenkosikazi yakhe u-Queen Mary batyelele i-India okokuqala, babamba itheko elikhulu leenkosi kunye nookumkanikazi base-Indiya abangaphezu kwama-400. Yayibizwa ngokuba yiDelhi Durbar. Ukondla iindwendwe ezingama-200,000, iivenkile zokubhaka zibeka izonka ezingama-20000 ngosuku, kwaye ngaphezulu kwe-1000 leenkomo kunye neegusha kuxhelwe kwisidlo ngasinye! Abalawuli abaninzi baseIndiya bafumana iimbasa zegolide kuMlawuli, kubandakanya uMaharaja waseMysore, uKrishnaraja Wodeyar IV.
Oololiwe abacocekileyo (ngo-1925) -ngo-Feb 3, 1925, uloliwe wokuqala wombane wase-India washiya iBombay's Victoria Terminus kwisikhululo saseKurla. Ngaloo nto, i-Indiya yaba lilizwe lesi-3 e-Asiya kwaye kuphela ngama-24 ehlabathini ukuzisa umbane kaloliwe.Idama elaludambisa iKaveri (1932) -UMlambo i-Kaveri uwela kumazantsi eKarnataka naseTamil Nadu. Umlambo wawusoloko uyintsikelelo, ugcina i-Mysore ichumile, kodwa, njengayo yonke eminye imilambo, yayihlala igcwala kwiimvula kwaye yomile ehlotyeni. Konke okutshintshileyo xa kwakhiwa idama ngaphesheya komlambo kunye nedama laseKrishna Raja Sagara (KRS). Idama linika amanzi okusela amaninzi kwisixeko sase Bangalore.
Intetho enkulu kaGandhiji (1942) -I-'Quit India Speech 'yayiyintetho eyenziwe nguGandhiji nge-8 ka-Agasti 1942, eGowalia Tank Maidan eBombay. UGandhiji ucele abantu ukuba balwe nolawulo lwaseBritane hayi ngokusebenzisa ubundlobongela, kodwa ngokungathobeli imithetho yabo. Kwiminyaka emihlanu kamva, ngo-Agasti 15, 1947, imfazwe engenabundlobongela yafumana iziphumo ezazifunwa nguGandhiji-i-Bhritane yashiya, kwaye i-India yazimela. Namhlanje, i-Gowalia Tank Maidan ibizwa ngokuba ngu-Agasti Kranti Maidan kwimemori yolo hlaziyo lunoxolo.
